body.name: CAPHAUS Tall Corner Shelf Stand, 4-Tier Display Shelves, Ladder Corner Wood Storage Plant Bookshelf with Metal Frame, Versatile Shelving Unit Bookcase for Home Office Space, Rustic Oak
features: 🌱 Stylish and Aesthetic Design - This corner shelf is not only a practical storage solution for any room but also adds a charming touch that blends seamlessly with your home decor. You can choose from two available colors - Rustic Oak and White - to suit your preferences.

🌱 Solid Construction - This corner shelf is a result of its matte black iron frames and P2 grade engineered board with a grain finish. The sturdy three-legged metal structure ensures long-term use, and the addition of a support leg at the bottom of the shelf makes it even sturdier.

🌱 Multifunctional and Versatile - This tall corner bookcase shelving unit is perfect for any corner in your living room, bedroom, home office, kitchen, hallway, balcony, or bathroom. It can be used as corner stand shelves, a small bookshelf, display shelf, plant stand, or flower rack, making it an ideal storage solution for limited spaces.

🌱 Spacious Geometric Shelves - This corner shelf offers ample storage space while utilizing the corner space effectively. Its fan-shaped shelves are perfect for displaying photos, plants, crafts, or even using it as a bookshelf. The smooth round edges ensure safety by protecting you and your family from getting scratched. The overall dimension of the shelf is 15.75 x 15.75 x 55.12 inches, and each shelf can hold up to 60 lbs.

🌱 Easy Assembly - Assembling this corner shelf is a breeze, all the required instructions and hardware are included in the package, ensuring a hassle-free installation process. CAPHAUS always provides you the best product to upgrade your life. Also, please do not hesitate to contact us by sending us a message through your Buyer Center, our customer service will help you rectify the issues encountered courteously and efficiently.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Loved them so much I ordered 2!
reviews.reviewText: So glad I found these. I measured so closely to find corner shelves that wouldn’t block our windows but be sturdy and aesthetically pleasing and not too bulky. That’s a lot in a shelf! These were perfect for holding my Le Creuset collection of cast iron pots and cookbooks! I love having them on display in my kitchen and they save me so much pantry space. I was able to get more cookbooks than I had previously just because of the extra storage. I love how good they look mixed in with my colorful pots. I highly recommend them!!

reviews.reviewText: This shelf lives in my head rent free. first of all its so cute but it also is actually very stable and can definitely hold some heavy weight. Definitely worth the money and its so easy to decorate and to hide cords too so its perfect if you want lights/electronics on the shelf.
